<plot>Subtitled ¨Entre el torb i la Gestapo¨ (between the Torb and the Gestapo). The story of the cooperation of the the French resistance, the people of Andorra and Catalunya in aiding the escape of the survivors of a RAF plane crash carrying essential information back to British Intelligence via Barcelona during the 2nd world war. The Torb is a fierce winter wind that blows through the mountain passes of Andorra between France and Spain. Based on true events.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?039375</url></doc>
